   BEIJING
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
SHARES in the manufacturer of one of the China's most famous products, the
'Forever' bicycle, are being offered to foreign investors, writes Tony
Walker in Beijing.
Sixty million 'B' shares - those denominated in US dollars - in the Shanghai
Yongjiu Bicycle Co. Ltd. were made available yesterday through a local
brokerage house and foreign underwriters.
